Application Theme:

* modern salon SaaS ERP
* premium but simple
* user friendly for non-technical salon users
* soft elegant UI
* minimal confusion
* clean layouts
* smooth rounded corners
* soft shadows
* mobile responsive

UI Standards:

* maintain consistent spacing
* maintain consistent typography
* avoid duplicated Tailwind styles
* use consistent icons
* keep interactions simple
* large clickable areas
* visually clean tables/forms

Always:

* use loading states
* use empty states
* use error states
* use responsive layouts

