All tables must use CommonTable.

Table Requirements:

* pagination
* sorting
* sortable icons
* per-column search
* global search
* filters
* row hover
* loading state
* skeleton loading
* empty state
* responsive design
* action column
* reusable row actions

Action Icons:
Use reusable common icons only:

* edit
* delete
* view
* more

Pagination:

* clean UI
* page numbers
* previous/next
* rows per page selector

Empty State:

* friendly UI
* salon themed
* visually engaging

---

# 6. Common Button Rules

All buttons must use CommonButton.

Support:

* primary
* secondary
* outline
* danger
* ghost
* success

Features:

* loading state
* disabled state
* icon support
* smooth animations
* consistent sizing

---

# 7. Common Modal Rules

All modals must use CommonModal.

Support:

* title
